{"title":"Oversized Tees","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"gods-favourite","title":"GOD'S FAVOURITE","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eCLOTH : 260 GSM FRENCH TERRY\r\nFIT : BOXY\r\nFRONT PRINT : EMBROIDERY\r\nBACK PRINT : EMBROIDERY\r\nQUALITY : COMBED \u0026amp; BIOWASHED\r\n\r\n\" MODEL HEIGHT 5'10, WEARING M SIZE \"\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStep into effortless streetwear energy with our Collar Oversized Tee—crafted for those who let their style speak louder than words. Featuring a bold front chest banding print with “DRIPSTU.”, this piece carries that clean, premium edge your fits have been waiting for. The back flex? A powerful “GODS FAVOURITE” statement print, dropping an unapologetic vibe that turns every sidewalk into a runway.\r\n\r\nCut in an oversized fit with structured collar detailing, this tee brings a mix of comfort and authority, making it perfect for pairing with cargos, denims, or shorts. Built from heavyweight cotton for durability and luxe feel, it’s more than just a tee—it’s a declaration.\r\n\r\nHighlights:\r\n\r\nOversized streetwear fit with collar\r\nFront chest DRIPSTU. banding print\r\nBack print: “GODS FAVOURITE” bold statement\r\nHeavyweight cotton, soft yet durable\r\n\r\nDesigned for all-day wear \u0026amp; elevated drip\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the vest inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the vest in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eVest with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853860884634,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853860917402,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853860950170,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853860982938,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853861015706,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853861048474,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"3XL","offer_id":46853861081242,"sku":"blinddrop2(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/77BF8F81-FC51-4B39-8AA6-D0D0E944F8B2.png?v=1769968735"},{"product_id":"idgaf-label","title":"IDGAF LABEL","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM.\r\nPUFF PRINT FRONT BACK\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTurn heads without saying a word. This 240 GSM heavyweight T-shirt speaks volumes with its bold front print: “Don’t Smile, Because It Happened Baby”—a savage nod to moving on like a boss. On the back? “Bitche Act Like You Are Not the Inspo”—because you know the truth. Made from premium cotton, it offers a structured fit, rich texture, and durability that matches your energy. Whether you’re flexing solo or throwing shade with style, this tee is the statement your wardrobe needs. Designed for the unapologetic, worn by the unforgettable.\r\n\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46853862490266,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853862523034,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853862555802,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853862588570,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853862621338,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"3XL","offer_id":46853862654106,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"S.","offer_id":46853862686874,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/2035F050-1F6B-4022-B3E6-FDA80C3EB2C9.png?v=1769972175"},{"product_id":"certified-lover-ltd-ed","title":"CERTIFIED LOVER","description":"\r\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\r\nEmbroidery work front\/back.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM black oversized T-shirt is crafted to offer a bold, streetwear-inspired aesthetic with premium details. Designed with a white cloth lining running from top to bottom, as well as from the front neck to the shoulder area, it brings a fresh touch to your look. The front features an embroidered logo, adding a touch of sophistication and an elevated vibe to the piece. On the back, the embroidered “Certified Lover” (that too in embroidery) print adds an extra layer of exclusivity. Perfect for those who appreciate luxury and street style, this T-shirt combines comfort, durability, and high-end craftsmanship.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407434906,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407467674,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407500442,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407533210,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881407598746,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407631514,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00022copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440426"},{"product_id":"code-9-flagged","title":"CODE-9 FLAGGED","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Fabric with Raglan Sleeves. Front \u0026amp; Back Print. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 260 GSM T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who like their style bold and unapologetic. Featuring classic raglan sleeves, it delivers enhanced comfort, mobility, and a distinct athletic-inspired silhouette. The front showcases the Drip Studios brand print with a clean, confident presence, while the back makes a powerful statement with the phrase “Are You Flagged and Certified Lover.” Crafted from high-quality French terry cotton, this tee offers durability, breathability, and all-day comfort. CODE 9 is made for individuals who wear their mindset as confidently as their style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and print longevity. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM fabric for a structured, premium feel. Raglan sleeves for improved comfort and a relaxed yet refined fit. Boxy, oversized silhouette suitable for both men and women. Unisex design crafted to complement diverse body types. Soft, breathable French terry cotton ensures lasting comfort and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407664282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407697050,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1