multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408843930,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408876698,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408909466,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408942234,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881408975002,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881409007770,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00497copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440585"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-military-green","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - MILITARY GREEN","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885004771482,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885004804250,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885004837018,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885004902554,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00005copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771439984"},{"product_id":"holy-flex","title":"HOLY FLEX","description":"\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M TEE.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e280 GSM premium French terry fabric for a substantial and durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit with full raglan sleeves for relaxed comfort and easy movement.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClassic black and white color blocking with a crisp white body and deep black sleeves.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLow-density front print featuring subtle script “Drip Studios” branding.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVertical “Drip Studios” screen print on sleeves for a bold yet minimal look.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImpactful Christ face graphic on the back with low-density print for a softer, artistic texture.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePiping work over the armhole area enhances structure and detailing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed finish for smooth texture and long-lasting quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the tee inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or fabric damage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCore Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTee with 280 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a premium, substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex article designed for versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable fabric ensures all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885005820058,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885005852826,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885005885594,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885005918362,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885005951130,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885005983898,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00348copy_11zon_1.jpg?v=1771440511"},{"product_id":"apex-god","title":"APEX GOD","description":"\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M TEE.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from premium 280 GSM French terry fabric for a structured, durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit with full raglan sleeves for enhanced comfort and movement.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTimeless white body paired with vibrant royal blue raglan sleeves.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBold “APEX GOD EST. 2023 DRIPSTU.” front graphic.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3D high-density front print delivers a strong visual and tactile impact.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePiping work over the armhole area adds elevated detailing and structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed finish for a smooth hand feel and long-lasting quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned as a statement streetwear piece with modern, assertive energy.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the tee inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve the fabric and print quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore the tee in a cool, dry place to avoid moisture damage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCore Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTee with 280 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a premium, substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit suitable for comfortable wear by both men and women.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex article designed for versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable fabric ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885006016666,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885006049434,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885006082202,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885006114970,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885006147738,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885006180506,"sku":"Reign2","price":1819.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/18E80B4D-0020-4DEF-9714-6E47FFA2DDB5.png?v=1769969007"},{"product_id":"stand-alone-jersey","title":"STAND ALONE JERSEY","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM\r\n100% French Terry Cotton\r\nBoxy Fit\r\nV - Neck\r\n3-D High Density Print Front\/Back\r\nWhite Fabric Piping on arms and V neck\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nCombed and Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOversized Boxy Fit V-Neck Jersey T-Shirt – \"Fear No One \/ Against All Odds\"\r\n\r\nStep into bold confidence with our oversized boxy fit V-neck jersey T-shirt, crafted from premium cotton for all-day comfort and effortless streetwear appeal. This relaxed silhouette features a front high-density print that reads \"FEAR NO ONE\", delivering a strong statement with a clean, elevated texture. On the back, the power continues with a matching high-density \"AGAINST ALL ODDS\" graphic—because your style should speak just as loud as your mindset.\r\n\r\n100% 260 GSM cotton for breathable comfort\r\n\r\nOversized, boxy fit with dropped shoulders for a modern streetwear look\r\n\r\nV-neckline for a relaxed yet refined edge\r\n\r\nHigh-density front and back prints for a bold, textured finish\r\n\r\nStatement graphics: \"FEAR NO ONE\" (front) \/ \"AGAINST ALL ODDS\" (back)\r\n\r\nWear it with confidence. Stand for something.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"L","offer_id":46885164712090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885164744858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885164777626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46885164843162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885164875930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885164908698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00177copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440486"},{"product_id":"rules-breaker","title":"RULES BREAKER II - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Fabric. Oversized Fit with Raglan Sleeves. Front Embroidery \u0026amp; Back Silicone Print. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis oversized 240 GSM waffle T-shirt from Drip Studios is built for comfort with a refined edge. Designed with raglan sleeves for enhanced mobility and a relaxed drape, it delivers a super-comfy yet decent silhouette. The front features a clean embroidered “Rules Breaker” logo, keeping it minimal and premium, while the back makes a bold statement with a high-quality silicone print reading “Rules Breaker.” Crafted from combed and bio-washed cotton waffle fabric, this tee offers breathability, texture, and lasting softness—perfect for elevated everyday wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM waffle fabric for a textured, premium feel. Oversized fit for a relaxed and comfortable silhouette. Raglan sleeves for improved movement and fit. Front embroidered logo with back silicone print for durability and style. Unisex design suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064570232986,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"titl