d, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064594219162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064594251930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064594284698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064594317466,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00130_copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772289251"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-melange-grey","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - MELANGE GREY","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare 