k. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064597168282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064597201050,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064597233818,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064597266586,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00173copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771439907"},{"product_id":"fear-no-one-waffle","title":"FEAR NO ONE - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Knit Fabric. Baggy Fit with Knit Collar. Front \u0026amp; Back Vinyl Prints. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 240 GSM waffle knit collar tee from Drip Studios blends structure with a relaxed, baggy silhouette for an elevated everyday look. Crafted from premium waffle fabric, it offers breathable comfort with a rich texture and lasting softness. The front features the Drip Signature Number 9 in high-quality vinyl print, keeping the design bold yet refined, while the back makes a powerful statement with “FEAR NO ONE” in durable vinyl printing. Finished with a knit collar for a clean, polished touch, this tee is combed and bio-washed to ensure superior comfort, shape retention, and long-term wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Do not bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain fabric quality and vinyl prints. Avoid direct ironing on prints. Store folded in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium waffle knit fabric for a textured, breathable feel. Perfect baggy fit for a relaxed yet structured silhouette. Knit collar for a clean and elevated finish. Front Drip Signature Number 9 vinyl print with bold “FEAR NO ONE” back print. High-quality vinyl printing for durability and sharp detailing. Unisex design suitable for all body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness and longevity.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079248724122,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079248756890,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079248789658,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079248822426,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079248855194,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079248887962,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_11zon_1.jpg?v=1771440357"},{"product_id":"resilient","title":"RESILIENCE","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy-Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Piping Work \u0026amp; Embroidery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM boxy-fit T-shirt is designed for a strong, confident everyday statement with premium comfort at its core. Crafted from 100% French terry cotton, it offers a soft yet substantial feel with excellent breathability and durability. The design is elevated with refined piping work across the shoulders and front, adding depth and structure to the silhouette. Premium embroidery detailing on both the front and back enhances the overall craftsmanship, delivering a clean yet bold aesthetic. Finished with combed and bio-washed fabric, this tee ensures lasting softness, shape retention, and all-day wearability.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Do not iron directly on embroidery. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium, heavyweight feel. Boxy fit for a relaxed and modern silhouette. Piping work across shoulders and front for elevated detailing. Front and back embroidery for a refined, high-quality finish. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Combed and bio-washed fabric for superior softness, durability, and long-lasting comfort.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":47079340507290,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079340540058,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079340572826,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079340605594,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079340638362,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":47079340671130,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00511copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440397"},{"product_id":"tempting","title":"TEMPTING","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Dual-Tone Colors. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Puff Print. Made for Club \u0026amp; House Parties.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is designed to blend soft aesthetics with bold, nightlife-ready detailing. Available in two refined shades—Baby Pink and Off-White—it delivers a clean yet statement-driven look. Crafted from premium French terry cotton, the fabric offers a smooth, substantial feel with breathable comfort and durability. Made specially for club and house parties, the front features a minimal printed logo for a refined finish, while the back stands out with a bold puff print reading \u003cstrong\u003e“AGAIN TEMPTED”\u003c\/strong\u003e alongside the signature \u003cstrong\u003e9\u003c\/strong\u003e, adding depth, texture, and standout appeal under lights. Combed and bio-washed for lasting softness, this tee is built for elevated after-dark wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve the puff print texture. Do not iron directly on the print. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium, heavyweight feel. Baby Pink and Off-White colorways crafted for night-out styling. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit ideal for club and house parties. Front logo print with bold “AGAIN TEMPTED” and 9 puff print on the back. High-quality puff printing for a textured, high-impact finish. Combed and bio-washed fabric for superior softness, durability, and shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079354466458,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079354499226,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079354531994,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079354564762,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079354597530,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079354630298,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00604copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440622"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-coffee","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - COFFEE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500127174810,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500127207578,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500127240346,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47500127273114,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00216copy_11zon_0c4b2494-11ce-42fd-935d-000267394055.jpg?v=1772289414"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Premium Puff \u0026amp; Screen Print. Exclusive Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is crafted to combine premium comfort with bold, statement-driven design. Built from heavyweight French terry cotton, the fabric delivers a smooth, structured feel while remaining breathable and durable for all-day wear. Designed as an exclusive limited-edition release, the front features the striking \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in a combination of premium puff and screen printing for layered texture and depth. The back carries the signature \u003cstrong\u003e09\u003c\/strong\u003e brand number in the same high-quality print finish, creating a cohesive, standout identity from every angle. Combed and bio-washed for long-lasting softness and shape retention, this tee is made for those who move with confidence and presence.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain print texture and fabric quality. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium heavyweight structure. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for everyday statement wear. Front “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” artwork in premium puff and screen print combination. Back brand number 09 executed in matching high-quality print finish. Exclusive limited-edition design for elevated street presence. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500129829018,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500129861786,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500129894554,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47500129960090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47500129992858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687033159834,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772289837"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-wine","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - WINE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47560478032026,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47560478064794,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47560478097562,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47560478130330,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/SWTS2398.webp?v=1773078848"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty-ii","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY II","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Heavyweight Fabric. High-Detail Puff Print Front \u0026amp; Back. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Exclusive YRM Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM premium T-shirt from the exclusive YRM limited-edition collection is designed to make a bold, unmistakable statement. Crafted from heavyweight fabric, it offers a structured yet breathable feel that delivers all-day comfort with a strong streetwear presence. The front and back feature intricately detailed \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in high-definition puff print, creating a striking raised texture that adds depth, dimension, and a premium visual impact. Designed for those who stand out effortlessly, this piece blends luxury aesthetics with everyday wearability. Combed and bio-washed for superior softness and long-lasting durability, it maintains its shape and finish over time while elevating your wardrobe with a powerful identity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric quality and puff print detailing. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM premium heavyweight fabric for a structured, high-end feel. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for statement streetwear. High-detail “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” puff print on both front and back for elevated texture and depth. Exclusive YRM limited-edition release for a distinctive look. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47682205384858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47682205417626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47682205450394,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","